---
import { site } from "../config/site";

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-brand-600 text-white font-bold text-sm">G</span>
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">{site.name}</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          {site.tagline}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">연락처</h3>
        <dl class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <dt class="w-12 shrink-0 text-slate-500">전화</dt>
            <dd><a href={site.contact.phoneHref} class="hover:text-brand-700">{site.contact.phone}</a></dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <dt class="w-12 shrink-0 text-slate-500">이메일</dt>
            <dd><a href={`mailto:${site.contact.email}`} class="hover:text-brand-700">{site.contact.email}</a></dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <dt class="w-12 shrink-0 text-slate-500">주소</dt>
            <dd>{site.contact.address}</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">영업시간</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li>{site.hours.weekday}</li>
          <li>{site.hours.lunch}</li>
          <li>{site.hours.weekend}</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 text-xs text-slate-500 space-y-1">
      <p>대표 {site.business.representative} · 사업자등록번호 {site.business.registrationNumber} · 보험대리점 등록번호 {site.business.insuranceAgencyNumber}</p>
      <p>&copy; {year} {site.name}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
